    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 ASME V&V 40 factors at MRL 2. Seven factors were formally assessed; six were scoped to MRL 2 minimum requirements. The discretization error factor achieved Gradation 1 against a required Gradation 2; however, the team judged that the supplementary experimental validation comparison (output comparison factor, 18% max deviation) provided sufficient compensating evidence to support an Accepted decision for the intended COU. The overall body of evidence is considered adequate for a Class II device at MRL 2 under the stated context of use.",
